          TattThat provides AI-generated tattoo previews for visualization purposes only. The previews are artistic renderings and may not perfectly represent how a real tattoo would appear. Always consult with a professional tattoo artist before getting actual ink.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Credits and Purchases</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          Credits are consumable and non-refundable once used. Unused credits do not expire. All purchases are final and processed through Apple's App Store according to their terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Content Guidelines</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          You may only upload photos you have the right to use. Do not upload inappropriate, illegal, or harmful content. We reserve the right to refuse service for violations.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          TattThat is provided "as is" without warranties. We are not liable for any decisions you make based on our previews. Tattoo decisions are personal and permanentâ€”always do your research.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          Questions? <a href="/support" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">Contact our support team</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
